{
  "video_id": "U_uSRHedmSs",
  "title": "Battle Over Bathrooms | Gender Revolution With Katie Couric (Bonus Scene)",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1300.0,
      "end_time": 2300.0,
      "text": "NARRATOR: There&#39;s a new battleground"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2300.0,
      "end_time": 3734.0,
      "text": "in this gender revolution--"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 3734.0,
      "end_time": 5133.0,
      "text": "bathrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 5133.0,
      "end_time": 8100.0,
      "text": "And nowhere is that battle more heated than in public schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8100.0,
      "end_time": 11667.0,
      "text": "Now, even the Supreme Court is set to weigh in on the case"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11667.0,
      "end_time": 15300.0,
      "text": "of Gavin Grimm, a transgender student in Virginia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15300.0,
      "end_time": 17433.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s fighting for the right to use the bathroom that"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17433.0,
      "end_time": 21166.0,
      "text": "corresponds to the gender he identifies as,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21166.0,
      "end_time": 24200.0,
      "text": "not the gender he was assigned at birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24200.0,
      "end_time": 26233.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not looking for separate but equal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26233.0,
      "end_time": 27600.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking for the same opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 27600.0,
      "end_time": 29633.0,
      "text": "that my peers enjoy every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 29633.0,
      "end_time": 33066.0,
      "text": "And that includes using the same restroom as any other student."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 33066.0,
      "end_time": 35033.0,
      "text": "NARRATOR: But one school in South Central LA"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 35033.0,
      "end_time": 37066.0,
      "text": "is already forging ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37066.0,
      "end_time": 39500.0,
      "text": "The Santee Education Complex High School."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39500.0,
      "end_time": 42500.0,
      "text": "In 2016 it opened what&#39;s considered"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42500.0,
      "end_time": 46500.0,
      "text": "the nation&#39;s first gender neutral, multi-stall restroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 46500.0,
      "end_time": 48333.0,
      "text": "A cause for celebration for some,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 48333.0,
      "end_time": 50600.0,
      "text": "a lightning rod for others."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 50600.0,
      "end_time": 53700.0,
      "text": "Santee is part of the LA Unified School District,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 53700.0,
      "end_time": 56834.0,
      "text": "which represents nearly 1,100 schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 56834.0,
      "end_time": 60600.0,
      "text": "and more than 640,000 students."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60600.0,
      "end_time": 63734.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a district that&#39;s been on the front lines of this issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 63734.0,
      "end_time": 66367.0,
      "text": "for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 66367.0,
      "end_time": 69367.0,
      "text": "The LA Unified School District has had transgender-affirming"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 69367.0,
      "end_time": 71734.0,
      "text": "policies since 2005."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 71734.0,
      "end_time": 73433.0,
      "text": "NARRATOR: That was more than a decade"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73433.0,
      "end_time": 76367.0,
      "text": "before President Obama told schools across the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 76367.0,
      "end_time": 79166.0,
      "text": "to open their bathrooms to transgender students"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 79166.0,
      "end_time": 81567.0,
      "text": "or face losing federal funds."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 81567.0,
      "end_time": 83467.0,
      "text": "The policy that we wrote 10 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83467.0,
      "end_time": 86834.0,
      "text": "was inspired by a family with a transgender first grader."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 86834.0,
      "end_time": 90133.0,
      "text": "The policy is actually pretty simple, that our transgender"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 90133.0,
      "end_time": 93066.0,
      "text": "students can access all facilities based on"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93066.0,
      "end_time": 94767.0,
      "text": "their affirmed gender identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 94767.0,
      "end_time": 97934.0,
      "text": "In LA Unified a student who is transgender"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 97934.0,
      "end_time": 102600.0,
      "text": "can change their name, their pronoun, and access facilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102600.0,
      "end_time": 104800.0,
      "text": "NARRATOR: It&#39;s a whole new world for educators."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104800.0,
      "end_time": 107700.0,
      "text": "So LA Unified trains them in everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107700.0,
      "end_time": 110867.0,
      "text": "from roll call in homeroom, diplomas at graduation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110867.0,
      "end_time": 114667.0,
      "text": "and, yes, the question of who can use which bathroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114667.0,
      "end_time": 117367.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to do a little test."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117367.0,
      "end_time": 119567.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s going to be some slides that come up"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119567.0,
      "end_time": 121700.0,
      "text": "and I just want you to call out the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121700.0,
      "end_time": 123867.0,
      "text": "in the slide, what is the bathroom that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123867.0,
      "end_time": 125667.0,
      "text": "would probably direct them to."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125667.0,
      "end_time": 130333.0,
      "text": "So if a student named John comes back from spring vacation"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130333.0,
      "end_time": 132867.0,
      "text": "and says my name is April and I would like you to refer"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132867.0,
      "end_time": 136633.0,
      "text": "to me by she and her, we sit down with this student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136633.0,
      "end_time": 138533.0,
      "text": "usually a counselor will talk to them"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138533.0,
      "end_time": 140900.0,
      "text": "and ask them what&#39;s going on, how long have"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140900.0,
      "end_time": 142200.0,
      "text": "you been feeling like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142200.0,
      "end_time": 144166.0,
      "text": "We make a plan with that student."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144166.0,
      "end_time": 145734.0,
      "text": "What is it that you need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145734.0,
      "end_time": 150633.0,
      "text": "Do you want to change how you&#39;re known at school completely?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150633.0,
      "end_time": 152567.0,
      "text": "Do you want us to change the name on the roster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152567.0,
      "end_time": 155100.0,
      "text": "Which are things that we&#39;re capable of doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155100.0,
      "end_time": 159133.0,
      "text": "When a student is transitioning and they meet with their school"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159133.0,
      "end_time": 161600.0,
      "text": "and they talk about their identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161600.0,
      "end_time": 165500.0,
      "text": "as something that is affirmed, is deeply rooted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165500.0,
      "end_time": 168100.0,
      "text": "it is consistent, it is persistent."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168100.0,
      "end_time": 172367.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t be transgender just for fifth period PE to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172367.0,
      "end_time": 173867.0,
      "text": "access to the locker room."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 173867.0,
      "end_time": 177867.0,
      "text": "We would not allow that because it needs to be genuine."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 177867.0,
      "end_time": 182667.0,
      "text": "And if the administrator has a reasonable suspicion"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 182667.0,
      "end_time": 186300.0,
      "text": "that the request is not legitimate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 186300.0,
      "end_time": 188867.0,
      "text": "they do not have to honor it."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188867.0,
      "end_time": 192800.0,
      "text": "The situation of a student, a male student--"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 192800.0,
      "end_time": 196200.0,
      "text": "interestingly we only seem to worry about our male students--"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 196200.0,
      "end_time": 198500.0,
      "text": "but a male student pretended to be transgender"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 198500.0,
      "end_time": 201200.0,
      "text": "so he can, for predatory reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 201200.0,
      "end_time": 204400.0,
      "text": "have access to a female facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 204400.0,
      "end_time": 206400.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s rather ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 206400.0,
      "end_time": 209367.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve heard all kinds of fears expressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 209367.0,
      "end_time": 211100.0,
      "text": "just through the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 211100.0,
      "end_time": 214066.0,
      "text": "None of those fears have ever been realized."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 214066.0,
      "end_time": 215667.0,
      "text": "Ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 215667.0,
      "end_time": 219433.0,
      "text": "We have never had the type of fearful misconduct"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219433.0,
      "end_time": 222333.0,
      "text": "that people talk about with our transgender students."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 222333.0,
      "end_time": 225834.0,
      "text": "That has never happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 225834.0,
      "end_time": 230333.0,
      "text": "Last year I got 17 phone calls in three days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 230333.0,
      "end_time": 232367.0,
      "text": "from elementary schools, mind you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 232367.0,
      "end_time": 234467.0,
      "text": "that had transgender students whose"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 234467.0,
      "end_time": 236867.0,
      "text": "parents wanted them to be able to attend"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 236867.0,
      "end_time": 238433.0,
      "text": "schools authentically."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 238433.0,
      "end_time": 242266.0,
      "text": "There are so many more students who are coming out now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 242266.0,
      "end_time": 245333.0,
      "text": "just because of the national conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 245333.0,
      "end_time": 247734.0,
      "text": "When we talk to families we can tell them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 247734.0,
      "end_time": 249467.0,
      "text": "we will be one of the most affirming school"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249467.0,
      "end_time": 251433.0,
      "text": "districts in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 251433.0,
      "end_time": 256300.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a promise that I am fortunate to be able to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 256300.0,
      "end_time": 259734.0,
      "text": "on behalf of all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 259733.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263633.0,
      "text": "I do believe that, as a country, we need to make space"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 263633.0,
      "end_time": 266400.0,
      "text": "for people who have more fluidity around their gender"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 266400.0,
      "end_time": 267867.0,
      "text": "or people who are transgender."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 267867.0,
      "end_time": 269467.0,
      "text": "Kind of break that rigidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 269467.0,
      "end_time": 273734.0,
      "text": "So I believe that, as a school district and as a community"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 273734.0,
      "end_time": 277867.0,
      "text": "and as people who care about others, that the more that we"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 277867.0,
      "end_time": 280867.0,
      "text": "can do to help people be more of who they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 280867.0,
      "end_time": 283033.0,
      "text": "the more they&#39;re going to be able to be engaged"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 283033.0,
      "end_time": 285867.0,
      "text": "in their education, follow their dreams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 285867.0,
      "end_time": 287467.0,
      "text": "and be more of who they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 287467.0,
      "end_time": 297467.0,
      "text": "Our goal is to help people be more of who they are, not less."
    }
  ]
}